title: The Maze Runner Series
description:
The Maze Runner Series by James Dashner consisting of the 4 novels in epub format and an exclusive book The Maze Runner Files , a 50+ page collection of classified records and concealed information from the world of the New York Times bestselling Maze Runner series in pdf format . The Maze Runner series is a pentalogy and a 5th novel The Fever Code will be released in 2016
Enjoy it Guys and keep seeding :)
